sources.description:
An investigator looks into the activities of a movie producer he believes is involved in smuggling Asians into the U.S.

a.k.a: Yellow Cargo
Director & Writer: Crane Wilbur 
Stars: Conrad Nagel, Eleanor Hunt, Vince Barnett
